Package: bshazard
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Smoothing of the Hazard Function
Version: 1.2
Date: 2024-05-10
Author: Paola Rebora,Agus Salim, Marie Reilly
Maintainer: Paola Rebora <paola.rebora@unimib.it>
Depends: R(>= 3.3.3),splines,survival,Epi
Description: The function estimates the hazard function non parametrically from a survival object (possibly adjusted for covariates). 
	     The smoothed estimate is based on B-splines from the perspective of generalized linear mixed models. Left truncated and right censoring data are allowed. 
	     The package is based on the work in Rebora P (2014) <doi:10.32614/RJ-2014-028>.
